OL,3,CShoplifter jailed after stealing more
OL,4,Cthan 790 Cadbury's Creme Eggs
OL,6,FA shoplifter who targeted shops across
OL,7,Fthe South East, stealing nearly 800
OL,8,FCadbury's Creme Eggs has been jailed.
OL,10,FLayton Richards, 29, targeted shops
OL,11,Facross Hampshire, Dorset and West
OL,12,FSussex, including 13 Co-Op stores.
OL,14,FDuring his spree, Richards stole a
OL,15,Ftotal of #3463.96 worth of produce and
OL,16,Fproducts from 19 different stores,
OL,17,Fincluding a total of 798 Cadbury's
OL,18,FCreme Eggs.
