OL,6,F"We have been working in strong
OL,7,Fpartnership with retailers regarding
OL,8,Foffenders who repeatedly target stores
OL,9,Fand victims with their persistent, and
OL,10,Foften intimidating, criminality.
OL,12,F"As a result of this collaboration
OL,13,Fwith retail partners, we have been
OL,14,Fable to ensure that we are sharing
OL,15,Finformation and evidence more
OL,16,Feffectively, resulting in stronger
OL,17,Fcases being presented to the Crown
OL,18,FProsecution Service.
