OL,6,F"We want to continue sending the
OL,7,Fmessage to repeat offenders that their
OL,8,Fbehaviour, and the impact it has on
OL,9,Fits victims, is not acceptable, while
OL,10,Falso receiving any support they
OL,11,Frequire to help steer them away from
OL,12,Fshoplifting.
OL,14,F"It is important that we continue to
OL,15,Ffocus on retail crime, protecting
OL,16,Fvictims and ensuring that offenders
OL,17,Fare held to account for their
OL,18,Fcriminality."
