OL,6,FSouthern Co-Op Loss Prevention &
OL,7,FSecurity Manager Gareth J Lewis said:
OL,8,F"This outcome is yet another positive
OL,9,Fexample of our ongoing collaborative
OL,10,Fwork with Hampshire Police.
OL,12,F"The only way for the business
OL,13,Fcommunity to tackle the evidenced
OL,14,Fincrease in retail crime and the
OL,15,Fissues that drive the individuals
OL,16,Foffending, is to work together and to
OL,17,Fprovide the police (and other
OL,18,Fagencies), with the information and
OL,19,Fevidence required."
